import React from 'react'
import { Flex, Box } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import { IconButton } from '@chakra-ui/core'

const ThemeSelector = () => (
  <Box>
    <IconButton icon='sun' />
  </Box>
)

const SignIn = () => (
  <Flex>
    <Box>
      <ThemeSelector />
    </Box>
  </Flex>
)

export default SignIn
